{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<mspace>","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"\n    <ol>\n        <li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\">MathML Reference</a></strong>\n\n        \n            </li><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\">&lt;math&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\">&lt;menclose&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/merror\">&lt;merror&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\">&lt;mfenced&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\">&lt;mfrac&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\">&lt;mi&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\">&lt;mn&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\">&lt;mo&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\">&lt;mover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\">&lt;mpadded&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\">&lt;mphantom&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mroot\">&lt;mroot&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\">&lt;ms&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msqrt\">&lt;msqrt&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\">&lt;mstyle&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\">&lt;mtable&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\">&lt;mtd&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\">&lt;mtext&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\">&lt;mtr&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\">&lt;munder&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\">&lt;munderover&gt;</a></li>\n        \n            <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/semantics\">&lt;semantics&gt;</a></li>\n        \n\n        \n    </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>MathML&lt;mspace&gt;元素用来表示一段空白，空白的大小由它自身的属性决定。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"class_id_style\">class, id, style</dt>\n <dd>用来供<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">样式表</a>使用。</dd>\n <dt id=\"depth\">depth</dt>\n <dd>空白在基线下方的高度&nbsp;(参阅&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\">length</a>).</dd>\n <dt id=\"height\">height</dt>\n <dd>空白在基线上方的高度&nbsp;(参阅&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\">length</a>).</dd>\n <dt id=\"linebreak\">linebreak</dt>\n <dd>Indicates a line-break at the space. Possible values: <code>auto</code> (default value), <code>newline</code>, <code>nobreak</code>, <code>goodbreak</code>, <code>badbreak</code>.<br>\n Starting with MathML 3, it is preferred to use <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code> to control linebreaking.</dd>\n <dt id=\"mathbackground\">mathbackground</dt>\n <dd>用来设置背景色，可以使用<code><strong>#rgb</strong></code>、<strong><code>#rrggbb</code></strong>或者<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/color_value\">HTML 颜色名</a>。</dd>\n <dt id=\"width\">width</dt>\n <dd>空白的宽度 (参阅&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\">length</a>).</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>注意，一些像<code>mathcolor</code>、<code>mathvariant</code>或<code>dir</code>这种常用的属性在<code>&lt;mspace&gt;</code>上是无效的。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mspace</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">depth</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>40px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">height</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>20px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>mspace</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">width</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>100px<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>math</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.mspace\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 3.0<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">mspace</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Current specification</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML2/chapter3.html#presm.mspace\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MathML 2.0<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">mspace</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial specification</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"mathml.elements.mspace","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko说明","title":"Gecko 说明","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/MathML3/chapter3.html#presm.lbindent.attrs\" rel=\" noopener\">Indentation attributes</a> 暂时没有实现 (for Gecko see <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=534962\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;534962</a>).</li>\n <li>从 Gecko 23.0 (Firefox 23.0 / Thunderbird 23.0 / SeaMonkey 2.20)开始实现了对<code>width</code>属性负值的支持。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mphantom\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mphantom&gt; (en-US)</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"Gecko 说明","id":"gecko说明"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"相关链接"}],"summary":"MathML<mspace>元素用来表示一段空白，空白的大小由它自身的属性决定。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<mspace>","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"<mspace>","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<mspace>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/mathml/element/mspace","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/mathml/element/mspace/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element","title":"MathML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace","title":"<mspace>"}],"pageTitle":"<mspace> - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}